N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.34 - Operation of tank vehicles restricted

State Regulations

No tank vehicle shall be operated in or upon the airport
unless approved as to equipment, construction, and condition by the airport
operator. Notes
